name: 2023 IEEE The 5th International Conference on Electronics Communication Technologies (IEEE ICECT 2023)
content: Publications: Accepted and presented papers in ICECT 2023 will be published in the IEEE conference proceedings, achieved to be included in IEEE Xplore, which will be indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus. All previous ICECT proceedings have been successfully published, and almost all have been indexed by EI Compendex, SCOPUS.
